ygData.messageBody:
The level 16th pet and 20pet are found in the Grobb Shadow Knight guild. As for hunting grounds I would suggest sticking to Oasis until 20 or at 18 or so you could move to Lake Rathe and hunt the undead at night and gnolls in the day.

Naeeldar Dark Elf Necromancer of the 33rd Circle
